data.description: Gorgeous ranch home with over 2200 sq feet! Two different spaces for entertaining, plenty of storage, office, large master suite with gas fireplace (for those upcoming winter nights), and no lack of yard! All appliances included! The open floor plan makes this home perfect for entertaining / hosting the family for the upcoming holidays. Call to schedule your private tour!
